Package: audiowmark-desktop
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: huddx01
Uploaders: Sojuzstudio
Homepage: https://github.com/huddx01/audiowmark-desktop
Description: Desktop GUI for audiowmark audio watermarking
 A PyQt6-based desktop application for adding and detecting
 invisible audio watermarks using audiowmark. Includes a
 bundled audiowmark binary — no separate installation required.
Depends: python3, python3-pyqt6
Recommends: ffmpeg
